to advising unsuccessful
applicants to the job.

125
00:05:22,130 --> 00:05:24,030
But in fact, it's really
an important stage.

126
00:05:24,030 --> 00:05:26,969
Because in many cases, it
really is a small world.

127
00:05:26,970 --> 00:05:29,160
And that one applicant
that never heard back

128
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:33,500
